## agent-sync conventions

All coordination memos live under:

`/.orchestration/runtime/agent-sync/`

### Memo requirements

Include:

- Date
- Audience (`@integrator` etc.)
- Status (`ready-to-consume` etc.)
- Branch + SHA (when applicable)

### Synapse role tags

Use project-specific audience tags where useful:

- `@artifact_orchestrator`
- `@requirements_strategist`
- `@customer_researcher`
- `@market_intelligence_analyst`
- `@competitive_intelligence_analyst`
- `@gtm_strategist`
- `@business_case_analyst`
- `@technical_architect`
- `@security_architect`
- `@pitch_deck_strategist`
- `@product_critic`
- `@executive_editor`
- `@integrator`

### Handoffs

When your work is safe for others to build on, post a `ready-to-consume` memo.

